---

<style>
  .contact-section {
    padding: 3rem 15rem;
    background-color: #fff;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  h1 .highlight {
    color: #197052;
  }

  .contact-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: nowrap; /* Ensures they stay next to each other */
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .contact-card {
    display: flex;
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 10px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    width: 50%;
    align-items: stretch;
    border-left: 8px solid #197052;
  }

  .contact-info {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .contact-info h3 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .contact-info p {
    margin: 0.2rem 0;
    color: #555;
  }

  .contact-image {
    flex: 1;
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    object-fit: cover;
    min-width: 130px;
  }

  .contact-card p strong {
    color: black;
  }
</style>

<section class="contact-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Dit zijn onze <span class="highlight">contactpersonen</span></h1>
    <p>
      Heb je vragen over de introductie, wil je meer weten over lidmaatschap of heb je andere vragen? Neem gerust contact met ons op! <br>
      We staan klaar om je te helpen, dus aarzel niet om een bericht te sturen!
    </p>

    <div class="contact-grid">
      {contacts.map(contact => (
        <div class="contact-card">
          <div class="contact-info">
            <h3>{contact.name}</h3>
            <p><strong>{contact.role}</strong></p>
            <p>ðŸ“§ {contact.email}</p>
            <p>ðŸ“ž {contact.phone}</p>
          </div>
          <img src={contact.image} alt={contact.name} class="contact-image" />
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
